Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.50,0:00:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離目標還有五海浬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.30,0:00:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“塞庫羅普斯”小隊出發準備好了沒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.70,0:00:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.10,0:00:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水艙注水完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.01,0:00:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2號 4號 1號 3號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打開艙門 “塞庫羅普斯”小隊出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.76,0:01:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體注意 維持150尺的深度 前往目標地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.17,0:01:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.67,0:01:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比預定時間晚了15分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.97,0:01:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體速率提高30
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.87,0:01:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,登陸時間還是15:00不變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.68,0:01:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海上起霧了 氣溫零下12度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.65,0:01:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米舍 暖身是好 但別太過量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.25,0:01:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前方雷達反應有暖流 是海底通道 我想是可以通過的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.36,0:01:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加西亞 米舍 你們照預定行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.10,0:01:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我與安迪進洞去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.90,0:01:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.25,0:02:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩台敵機偷襲 兩台敵機偷襲 地面部隊展開防禦網
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.86,0:02:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,運輸班！搬運工作動作快些！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.40,0:02:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有2個 再快也得再十分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.90,0:02:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五分鐘內完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.10,0:02:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辦不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.88,0:03:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 運輸機中找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.55,0:03:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這兒也是一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.15,0:03:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地上的人似乎都是幌子用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.85,0:03:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安迪 你那兒狀況如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.35,0:03:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,升降機離出口不遠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.16,0:03:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先去調查 小心不要受傷喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.86,0:03:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.90,0:04:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 他們在準備了太空梭  一般不可能用傳送帶送進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.94,0:04:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以傳送影像過來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.64,0:04:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有電子干擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.04,0:04:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.44,0:04:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阻止發射 允許用火箭炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.31,0:04:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.42,0:04:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被敵人困住了 動不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.32,0:04:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來掩護 稍等片刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.22,0:04:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們已經進入倒計時了 來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.43,0:04:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我準備強攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.43,0:04:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 安迪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安迪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.77,0:05:40.86,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}離戰場還有幾英里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.50,0:05:49.00,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Can't you see that you are sweet？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.00,0:05:57.90,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Oh let me love you so
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.00,0:06:12.20,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}見上げる空は遠いけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.00,0:06:19.00,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}抱えきれない夢がある
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.00,0:06:20.20,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そうよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.60,0:06:26.20,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}創られた世界の中を
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.00,0:06:34.00,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}抜け出して 自由になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.00,0:06:41.00,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}走り続けて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.00,0:06:47.20,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}空に屆けば
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.00,0:06:52.00,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}風になれると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.00,0:06:57.20,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そう信じてるから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.00,0:07:05.20,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I never give up forever
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.74,0:07:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾 快來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.54,0:07:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天吃漢堡哦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.81,0:07:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是保健蛋白質呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.31,0:07:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已是第三次了 真不好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.52,0:07:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.42,0:07:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真好 什麼都吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.72,0:07:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽說 因為戰爭的關係而物資短缺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.76,0:07:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭是聯邦與吉翁在打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.47,0:07:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和這個衛星殖民地無關吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.17,0:07:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為運輸艦發生問題了 你們若不吃就讓我吃吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.77,0:08:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你看個好東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.69,0:08:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是聯邦軍的軍級章 是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.79,0:08:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可摸摸嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.19,0:08:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一下子而已哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.89,0:08:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哥哥是機動戰士的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.73,0:08:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開那東西嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.13,0:08:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也吃了苦頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.43,0:08:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真帥 聯邦的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.14,0:08:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全是騙人的 聯邦哪來的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.91,0:08:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人什麼也不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.41,0:08:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是不是白癡呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.62,0:08:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分明是有機動戰士 少不懂裝懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.12,0:08:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦根本沒有機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.13,0:08:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前是沒有 但現在有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.63,0:08:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.16,0:08:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,健說得對 我有看過機動戰士的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.70,0:09:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因我爸爸在運輸公司工作 以前在港口看過的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.01,0:09:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在Side7搬運中的聯邦的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.11,0:09:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.28,0:09:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那部機動戰士又黑又大 好像很厲害的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.48,0:09:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,證據呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.79,0:09:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,證據？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.19,0:09:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們說的全都是謊話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.79,0:09:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那軍級章一定也是假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.59,0:09:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.73,0:09:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.73,0:09:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這小矮子 少囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.04,0:09:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種女人真討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.91,0:09:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀！再沒比她性格更壞的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.11,0:09:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要讓她臣服於我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.00,0:09:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的啦 她那麼能說會道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.00,0:09:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若有證據就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.10,0:09:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士的照片或錄影帶之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.33,0:10:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾 你說過你今天要見你爸是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.76,0:10:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.98,0:10:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.48,0:10:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回來啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.56,0:10:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是要直接去港口的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.16,0:10:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘了東西 我走啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.00,0:10:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去港口拍些聯邦的機動戰士照來當證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.70,0:10:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是這樣 便給你軍級章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.32,0:11:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾•佛烈德•伊茲魯哈 11歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.33,0:11:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通行代號0039295MC
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.27,0:11:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你爸的船在23號門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.87,0:11:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再過十分鐘左右便會入港
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.97,0:11:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.53,0:12:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要說是機動戰士 連個影子形狀也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.37,0:12:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在這裏幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.47,0:12:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在找廁所 附近有沒有？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.08,0:12:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出了電梯通道 第5個入口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.05,0:12:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.55,0:12:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可別尿得滿地啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.85,0:12:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 是否有什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.15,0:12:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是個迷路的小孩 不用在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.16,0:12:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快些檢查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.64,0:13:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 今天怎這麼安靜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.61,0:13:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽呢？還好吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.41,0:13:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬馬虎虎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.41,0:13:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬馬虎虎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.92,0:13:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼變化 和平時一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.22,0:13:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.72,0:13:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,考試考得如何？自然科學的成績
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.02,0:13:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬馬虎虎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.43,0:13:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概考幾分？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.36,0:13:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.46,0:13:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,數學與化學呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.76,0:13:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-和D
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.25,0:13:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,理科很行嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.87,0:13:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 這交給媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.28,0:13:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是封重要的信 千萬別掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.85,0:13:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 有件事想拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.63,0:14:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 沒事吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.96,0:14:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有受傷？不得了 鼻子和額頭都紅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.57,0:14:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾 你是亞爾吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.87,0:14:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我啦！克莉斯汀娜•馬克其 克莉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.35,0:14:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.85,0:14:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎會忘呢？克莉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.85,0:14:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是去了地球嗎？何時回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.75,0:14:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天中午 現在正將行李搬進屋裏去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得了 行李會打濕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.93,0:15:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.13,0:15:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,車子座位上的包裹和資料交給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.00,0:15:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.31,0:15:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有關安全方面的工作？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.82,0:15:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然被調來這裏 搞得我忙壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.42,0:15:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還托媽媽去政府機關辦手續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.03,0:15:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一會兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.17,0:15:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽不在 連東西放哪兒都不知了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.57,0:15:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就穿這個先忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.15,0:15:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾 奶茶好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.95,0:15:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.19,0:16:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請喝 若糖不夠再加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.23,0:16:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.91,0:16:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若要晚回來 也得早點打電話告訴我呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.52,0:16:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽還以為你出事了 很擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.62,0:16:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.46,0:16:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的狀況沒變嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.55,0:16:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.67,0:16:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要我將那信封交給你 說是信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.18,0:17:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.28,0:17:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是還有剩下嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.68,0:17:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和爸爸一起吃過了 所以不太餓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.69,0:17:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會再想吃 媽媽可不理你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.62,0:17:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.22,0:17:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一會兒 就來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.33,0:17:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天不是有體育課嗎？免得忘了 今晚就把它放進書包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.37,0:17:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.67,0:17:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做完功課就快睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.77,0:17:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.47,0:17:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天怎麼這麼聽話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.17,0:17:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.40,0:19:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攝影偷拍狂！睡得可好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.11,0:19:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.68,0:19:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學校真那麼沒趣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.48,0:19:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最沒趣 班主任又不會教課作業也多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.49,0:19:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還會罰人站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.49,0:19:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,常受罰嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.29,0:19:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾啦 此外 伙食又不好 廁所也髒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.63,0:19:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘是令人不悅的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.73,0:19:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種鬼地方還得去一年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.63,0:19:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中學 高中都是如此的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.04,0:19:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是以後的事 怎麼會知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.74,0:19:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回頭見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.01,0:19:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我托我爸爸帶我進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.10,0:19:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但昨天聯邦的軍隊沒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.12,0:19:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來的儘是些民間的船隻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.52,0:19:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嘛 只拍到貨櫃而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.53,0:20:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來 軍級章就不能給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.16,0:20:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.76,0:20:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的東西 真那麼想要嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.87,0:20:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將軍 元帥 軍曹 伍長 科長 部長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.07,0:20:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家隔壁玩具店中一元便可買到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.47,0:20:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了這些便宜貨而煩惱 真是白癡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.28,0:20:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.15,0:20:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.55,0:20:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是聯邦的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.96,0:20:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有吉翁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.92,0:21:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 比煙火還漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.06,0:21:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還會再來哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.76,0:21:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是渣古
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.86,0:21:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傷得很嚴重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.16,0:21:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向這邊來了 要撞上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.76,0:21:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要掉下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.36,0:21:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是要往西邊去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.30,0:21:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是要往森林公園去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.60,0:21:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾 你打算要做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.10,0:21:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要蹺課是不是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.51,0:23:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還很燙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.80,0:24:19.51,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}噓をついた夜には
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.51,0:24:25.51,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}眠れずに 怖かった
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.51,0:24:31.51,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どんな喧嘩をしても
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.51,0:24:38.51,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}次の日は 忘れていた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.51,0:24:46.51,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}空が 青いこと
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.00,0:24:53.51,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}それが 嬉しくて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:54.70,0:25:00.51,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか人を疑い
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.70,0:25:07.51,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生きる寂しさ知る事も
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.51,0:25:13.51,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}気がつかずに全てを
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.00,0:25:18.51,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}信じてた頃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:44.51,0:25:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還給我 快還給我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:47.51,0:25:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:50.51,0:25:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:51.40,0:25:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:53.51,0:25:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新接受的任命書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:56.51,0:25:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是秘密行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:58.51,0:26:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:00.51,0:26:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新人類用的機動戰士嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:10.70,0:26:14.20,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,茶色瞳孔中映出的景象
